1. Facebook -- there is a possibilty that Facebook's API may not return an e-mail address. Reason as reported by Facebook:

1a. No Email address on account 
1b. No confirmed email address on account 
1c. No verified email address on account 
1d. User entered a security checkpoint which required them to reconfirm their email address and they have not yet done so 
1e. Users's email address is unreachable 
1f. You also need the 'email' extended permission, even for users who have a valid, confirmed, reachable email address on file. 


Further details:  https://developers.facebook.com/bugs/298946933534016